*Nesreća* mu je stigla prerano. (Misfortune came to him too early.)

On nije mogao da izbegne *nesreću*. (He couldn't avoid the misfortune.)

Oni su potpuno zaboravili na prethodnu *nesreću*. (They completely forgot about the previous misfortune.)

Nažalost, *nesreća* se dogodila. (Unfortunately, the misfortune happened.)

Oni su se nadali da će zaobići *nesreću*. (They hoped to avoid the misfortune.)